  <brief_title>Safety Study of SD-101 (a Novel C Type Toll-like Receptor 9 (TLR9) Agonist) for the Treatment of Chronic Hepatitis C Virus (HCV) Infection</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase I, Randomized, Single-Blind, Placebo-Controlled Dose-Escalation Study of SD-101 to Assess the Safety, Pharmacodynamics, and Preliminary Evidence of Anti-Viral Effect in Subjects Diagnosed With Chronic Hepatitis C, Genotype 1</official_title>
