  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To determine safety, tolerability, and preliminary efficacy of escalating doses of SD-101
      alone and SD-101 plus ribavirin in subjects with chronic hepatitis C and no prior therapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
